title: Time Machine 11 Mission to WW2 (Choose Your Own Adventure).pdf
description:
Time Machine from the Publishers of Choose Your Own Adventure
It is the Year 1940
You have traveled back to Europe during World War II

You are hiding from German soldiers in the attic of a Warsaw house.  A young Jewish boy in the resistance movement offers to help you escape.

You must act quickly.  Do you risk your life on the streets of the Warsaw ghetto with your friend, or do you head out on your own?  Your decision can lead you to safety or leave you stranded in time!

ARE YOU READY TO FACE THE DANGER?

TIME MACHINE 11 Mission to World War II
by Susan Nanus and Marc Kornblatt
Illustrated by John Pierard
A Byron Press Book, published March 1986
